Name: Mega Cheer-Up Treat
Description: Consumption grants a special effect: receive triple clear rewards the next time you complete any Chaotic Realm dungeon. This effect doesn't apply to assist rewards, Bane Lord loot, or clear counts, and remains subject to the weekly Reforge Stone acquisition limit in Chaotic Realm.
